{"tid":2246181,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國低調承認藏南地區是印度一部分","createTime":"2020-10-17T00:00:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-17T02:36:11.000Z","uid":221827,"like":27,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"d379674fcf4774e53f1007b9ba068691d4ba9ac2","tid":2246181,"uid":221827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T00:00:27.000Z","msg":"新華社在15日煞有介事貼出宣傳海報，預告16日8點將會發佈一張重要地圖，令人揣測是不是與攻台有關。不到半日被人民網公開處刑，指責海報上的暗坎背景所顯示的藏南國界，竟然是印度主張的版本，以麥克馬洪線為界，迫到新華社急忙改圖，現在帖也刪掉了，連帶準備大做特做的那張捧習的扶貧地圖也要低調處理。<br />\n<br />\n這就是黨媒互咬。<br />\n<br />\n作者<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DgmeKuh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDgmeKuh.jpg&h=3635866b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00757df161577a577e3b72ccc1a0cfeea871b028","tid":2246181,"uid":191926,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T00:02:40.000Z","msg":"契哥2.0 印度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd1f8b34757045c3d914b130cc65f5fb22ac78cc","tid":2246181,"uid":1654,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T00:05:39.000Z","msg":"描述新華通訊社，簡稱新華社，是中華人民共和國主要國家通訊社，現為中華人民共和國<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">國務院</span></span>正部級直屬事業單位<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpoi8nkn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpoi8nkn.jpg&h=a396b79a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f0ded3788a0f2496da0a3e01e6273448fff61e22","tid":2246181,"uid":297997,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T00:06:03.000Z","msg":"想割少少地了事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"714bfb61c4176f7f608eb8456f13651abe023380","tid":2246181,"uid":155095,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd1f8b34757045c3d914b130cc65f5fb22ac78cc","tid":2246181,"uid":1